[h4 id=Config 
	" Config
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"You can download and modify a 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=premade windowsxp.cfg|href=/UserFiles/Info/638283187222055723)
	" file (change the paths to point to the correct files, with the Windows XP utilities .iso replaced with the name of the Windows XP utility disc .iso image you created or downloaded above).
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"You can optionally also make one yourself using the following specifications. If something is not specified, leave it at default. You may not get some of the options when you make a new config; if this happens, click "OK" to save it and then try editing it again.
	$LF
